<i>noun</i>: 호색 [호ː색], 춘정 [춘정], 춘심 [춘심], 정욕 [정욕], 정염 [정염], 음욕 [으묙], 육욕 [유굑], 욕정 [욕쩡] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호색 [호ː색]</dt><br>
<dd>lust; lewdness</dd><br>
<dd>남자가 여자와 육체적 관계를 맺는 것을 몹시 좋아하고 밝힘.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a man is extremely interested in and enjoys having a sexual relationship with a woman.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>춘정 [춘정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sexual desire; lust</dd><br>
<dd>남녀 사이에 성적으로 끌리는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>Feelings of sexual attraction between a man and a woman.</dd><br>
<dd>2. spring sentiments</dd><br>
<dd>봄의 정취.</dd><br>
<dd>The mood felt in spring.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>춘심 [춘심]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sexual desire; lust</dd><br>
<dd>남녀 사이에 성적으로 끌리는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>Feelings of sexual attraction between a man and a woman.</dd><br>
<dd>2. spring sentiments</dd><br>
<dd>봄에 느끼는 마음속의 생각이나 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>One's thoughts or feelings arising in spring.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정욕 [정욕]</dt><br>
<dd>lust</dd><br>
<dd>이성에게 느끼는 성적 욕망.</dd><br>
<dd>The sexual desire felt toward the opposite sex.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정염 [정염]</dt><br>
<dd>lust</dd><br>
<dd>불같이 일어나는 격렬한 욕정.</dd><br>
<dd>An intense sexual desire that arises like a fire.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>음욕 [으묙]</dt><br>
<dd>carnal desire; lust</dd><br>
<dd>음란한 욕심.</dd><br>
<dd>A sensual desire.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>육욕 [유굑]</dt><br>
<dd>sexual desire; lust</dd><br>
<dd>육체의 쾌락을 좇아 성적 관계를 맺고 싶어 하는 욕망.</dd><br>
<dd>The desire with which one pursues bodily pleasure and wants to have sex.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>욕정 [욕쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>1. desire; passion</dd><br>
<dd>순간적으로 생겨나는, 무엇을 바라거나 원하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>An instant surge of desire to hope for or want something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sexual desire; lust</dd><br>
<dd>이성에 대한 육체적인 욕망.</dd><br>
<dd>The desire to have sexual intercourse with the opposite sex.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>